#
# DEPLOYMENT SCENARIOS:
#   üèóÔ∏è  Guardian only: DEPLOY_ACCOUNTBLOX=true, example flags=false (default)
#   üè¶  Examples: Set example flags=true (for example contract testing)
#
# EXAMPLE CONTRACTS:
#   üè¶ SimpleVault: Example vault contract with Bloxchain integration
#   üè¶ SimpleRWA20: Example RWA token contract with Bloxchain integration
